*secret.yaml
*auth

# Vendored Helm subchart tarballs.
# Renovate bumps Chart.yaml/Chart.lock but never the tarball, and Helm renders
# from whatever is physically in charts/ — so a committed tarball silently
# overrides the pinned version and the upgrade never reaches the cluster
# (ArgoCD still reports Synced/Healthy). ArgoCD's repo-server runs
# `helm dependency build`, which resolves the correct version from Chart.lock.
infrastructure/monitoring/charts/*.tgz
